w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Lost-Vilage-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Lost-Vilage-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Lost-Vilage-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《失落的村庄》宣布了 2024 年版本的庞大阵容。</p><p>林肯郡音乐节将于今年 8 月 22 日至 25 日回归，众多知名表演者将登台演出，其中包括 Maribou State、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/floating-points">Floating Points</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-blessed-madonna">The Blessed Madonna 等</a>知名乐队。</p><p>加入他们的还有 Ben UFO、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/chaos-in-the-cbd">Chaos in the CBD</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/haai">HAAi</a> 、Horse Meat Disco、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/logic1000">Logic1000</a> 、Jyoty、Ross From Friends、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sherelle">Sherelle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sofia-kourtesis">Sofia Kourtesis</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hudson-mohawke">Hudson Mohawke</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/tsha-capricorn-sun-review-radar-3321627">TSHA</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yaeji">Yaeji</a> 。门票现已发售——请点击<a href="https://lostvillage.com/tickets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>购买。</p><p>节日还将举办“失落的剧院”，喜剧明星将登上舞台——过去的名字包括西蒙·阿姆斯特尔、菲尔·王、乔尔·多米特、凯瑟琳·瑞安和乔·莱塞特。失落的村庄将在“好奇心研究所”举办一系列讲座和现场采访；之前的演讲者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jayda-g">Jayda G</a> 、XL 老板<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/richard-russell">Richard Russell</a>和电影导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/irvine-welsh-offence-documentary-sky-2819802">Irvine Welsh</a> 。</p><p>请参阅下面迄今为止公布的完整阵容： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2w3ofxM1P3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max